    "body": "Hi, the following code will do the trick as you described.\r\nrun it in any cell, and will apply to all output blocks.\r\n\r\n```\r\n%%javascript\r\n\r\nwindow.scroll_flag = true\r\nwindow.scroll_exit = false\r\nwindow.scroll_delay = 2000\r\n\r\nfunction callScrollToBottom() {\r\n    setTimeout(scrollToBottom, window.scroll_delay);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction scrollToBottom() {\r\n    if (window.scroll_exit) {\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    if (!window.scroll_flag) {\r\n        callScrollToBottom();\r\n        return;\r\n    };\r\n    $(\".output_scroll\").each(function() {\r\n        $(this)[0].scrollTop = $(this)[0].scrollHeight;\r\n    });\r\n    callScrollToBottom();\r\n}\r\nscrollToBottom();\r\n```\r\n\r\nMoreover, prevent you want to disable it,\r\nyou can just execute the code `window.scroll_flag = flase` in browser console(F12).\r\nor you can modify the delay of the operation to 3s by type code `window.scroll_dalay = 3000`."
